  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Color mixing mechanics</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/50e5d300563b20ff8b7eaff70172a432.poster.avif?t=1753690922\" width=576 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/50e5d300563b20ff8b7eaff70172a432.webm?t=1753690922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/50e5d300563b20ff8b7eaff70172a432.mp4?t=1753690922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>You need to select and combine colors so that they match the color of the enemy. This way they take much more damage!</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelike experience</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/8398ef0c693bfab78d686ab945858f09.poster.avif?t=1753690922\" width=580 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/8398ef0c693bfab78d686ab945858f09.webm?t=1753690922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/8398ef0c693bfab78d686ab945858f09.mp4?t=1753690922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Combine passive and active abilities to create your own overpowered build and complete all levels despite permadeath!</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique art style</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/23d2e12e0efe7adea5ee45c646fedf2b.poster.avif?t=1753690922\" width=576 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/23d2e12e0efe7adea5ee45c646fedf2b.webm?t=1753690922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/23d2e12e0efe7adea5ee45c646fedf2b.mp4?t=1753690922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>The visuals in Clayers are inspired by a time when games were trying to look unusual</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Color mixing mechanics</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/50e5d300563b20ff8b7eaff70172a432.poster.avif?t=1753690922\" width=576 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/50e5d300563b20ff8b7eaff70172a432.webm?t=1753690922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/50e5d300563b20ff8b7eaff70172a432.mp4?t=1753690922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>You need to select and combine colors so that they match the color of the enemy. This way they take much more damage!</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelike experience</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/8398ef0c693bfab78d686ab945858f09.poster.avif?t=1753690922\" width=580 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/8398ef0c693bfab78d686ab945858f09.webm?t=1753690922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/8398ef0c693bfab78d686ab945858f09.mp4?t=1753690922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Combine passive and active abilities to create your own overpowered build and complete all levels despite permadeath!</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique art style</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2979020/extras/23d2e12e0efe7adea5ee45c646fedf2b.poster.avif?t=1753690922\" width=576 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.ste